        "content": "<p>Here is the theorem statement for reference, if anyone would like to suggest a potentially better structure.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/qchqr7uQTTbBfVmFbzAciyK2/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/qchqr7uQTTbBfVmFbzAciyK2/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/qchqr7uQTTbBfVmFbzAciyK2/image.png\"></a></div>",
